title="Frank Stajano">Frank Stajano</fr:link></fr:contributor></fr:authors></fr:frontmatter><fr:mainmatter><fr:p>Let <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[M]]></fr:tex> be an NFA with <html:span
xmlns:html="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"
style="white-space: nowrap"><fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[\epsilon ]]></fr:tex>-transitions</html:span>; then <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[\mathcal {L}{\mathopen {}\left (\mathcal {P}{\mathopen {}\left (M\right )\mathclose {}}\right )\mathclose {}}\subseteq  \mathcal {L}{\mathopen {}\left (M\right )\mathclose {}}]]></fr:tex>.</fr:p><fr:tree
